2. 定义 MyBatis Plus Sink 类，并实现 RichSinkFunction 接口：

```java
public class MyBatisPlusSink extends RichSinkFunction<List<Entity>> {

    private SqlSessionFactory sqlSessionFactory;
    private SqlSession sqlSession;
    private EntityMapper entityMapper;

    @Override
    public void open(Configuration parameters) throws Exception {
        super.open(parameters);

        // 初始化 MyBatis Plus
        sqlSessionFactory = new SqlSessionFactoryBuilder().build(Resources.getResourceAsStream("mybatis-config.xml"));
        sqlSession = sqlSessionFactory.openSession(true);

        // 获取 EntityMapper
        entityMapper = sqlSession.getMapper(EntityMapper.class);
    }

    @Override
    public void close() throws Exception {
        super.close();

        // 关闭 sqlSession
        sqlSession.close();
    }

    @Override
    public void invoke(List<Entity> entities, Context context) throws Exception {
        // 将实体列表插入数据库
        entityMapper.insertBatch(entities);
    }
}
```

