    }

Since the `execute(Params...)` method is deprecated as of API 30, you can use the `executeOnExecutor(Executor, Params...)` method with the `THREAD_POOL_EXECUTOR` instead. Update the `btnUp.setOnClickListener` code block as follows:

```java
btnUp.setOnClickListener(new View.OnClickListener() {
    @Override
    public void onClick(View v) {
        // Set the wifiModuleIp and wifiModulePort variables to the Raspberry Pi's IP address and SSH port, respectively
        MainActivity.wifiModuleIp = "192.168.1.100";
